ext-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>How do I return my items?</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="6" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706086827245" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706086827245"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>We can still cancel/edit your order as long as the order is not in transit. Please reach out to us by visiting our contact page. Make sure to include your order number. That way we are able to help get the concern resolved as soon as possible.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="5" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Accordion" data-key="accordion" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1706088732328" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-accordion" data-ver="2" data-id="1706088732328"><div data-accordion-group="" class="module " data-opendefault="0" data-opentab="1" data-single="0" data-bordercolor="rgba(255, 197, 225, 1)" data-bordersize="1px"><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="1" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732329" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732329"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>iDeal</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="1" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732337" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732337"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>iDeal is an online payment system used in the Netherlands. It allows customers to make secure payments directly from their bank accounts. When you choose iDeal at checkout, you are redirected to your online banking environment, where you can authorize and complete the payment. It's a direct and efficient way to pay for online purchases without the need for credit cards.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="2" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732319" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732319"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc="">Klarna: Shop now, pay later</div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="2" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732307" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732307"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Klarna is a payment service that allows you to make online purchases and pay for them later. When you choose Klarna at checkout, you can delay your payment or opt for installment plans. After placing your order, you receive your items, and Klarna sends you an invoice with the payment details.<br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706089149727" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706089149727"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><i>In cooperation with Klarna Bank AB (publ.), Sveavägen 46, 111 34 Stockholm, Sweden, we offer the following payment options. Payment is to be made to Klarna. Invoices: The payment period is 30 days from dispatch of the goods/ticket/ or, in the case of other services, provision of the service. The use of the payment methods invoice, installment purchase and direct debit requires a positive credit check. In this respect, we forward your data to Klarna for the purpose of address and credit checks as part of the purchase initiation and processing of the purchase contract. Please understand that we can only offer you those payment methods that are permitted based on the results of the credit check. Your personal data will be treated by Klarna in accordance with the applicable data protection regulations and in accordance with the information in Klarna's privacy policy.</i></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="3" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732292" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732292"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>PayPal</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="3" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732284" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732284"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>PayPal is an online payment platform that facilitates secure transactions between buyers and sellers. When you use PayPal at checkout, you can link your bank account, credit, or debit card to your PayPal account. Instead of sharing your financial information with the seller, you use your PayPal login. After choosing PayPal, you're redirected to log in and confirm the payment.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="4" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732340" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732340"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Credit Card</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="4" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732262" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732262"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>After selecting credit card payment you will be transferred to 3D Secure platform to fill in the data. If the transaction is authorized, the payment proceeds immediately and we can post your order the very next day.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.24px;">Our staff does not operate with your card data. The process is finished through online banking. We accept the following credit cards: Visa, Mastercard, Maestro, American Express.</span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="5" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732317" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732317"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Apple Pay</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="5" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732283" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732283"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Apple Pay is a mobile payment and digital wallet service. When choosing Apple Pay at checkout, you can complete your purchase using your iPhone, iPad, or Mac. Simply authenticate the payment with Touch ID or Face ID, and Apple Pay securely processes the transaction without the need to manually enter your card details.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="6" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088732294" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088732294"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Google Pay</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="6" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088732370" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088732370"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Google Pay is a digital wallet and online payment system. When you opt for Google Pay at checkout, you can use your Android device or a browser on your computer. After selecting Google Pay, follow the prompts to confirm your payment. Google Pay securely processes the transaction without revealing your card details to the seller.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="7" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706088994982" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706088994982"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Bancontact</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="7" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706088995003" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706088995003"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Bancontact is an electronic payment system used in Belgium. When selecting Bancontact at checkout, you can securely complete your online purchase by entering your Bancontact card details. The payment is then processed directly from your linked bank account.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="8" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1706089001432" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1706089001432"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Bank transfer</p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:none"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="8" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706089001422" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706089001422"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Bank transfer is a traditional and secure method of online payment. When you choose bank transfer at checkout, you will receive the seller's banking details. To complete the purchase, you manually initiate a transfer from your bank account to theirs.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><div class="gf_clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;</script>
